{"type": "article", "id": 10344, "title": "Erik Spiekermann x Unamono 围巾", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-03T08:32:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235519CiwAblSKUuohMRQr.png", "contents": "\n\n<h2 style=\"white-space:normal;\">\r\n\tScarves by Erik Spiekermann\r\n</h2>\r\n<p class=\"p2\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">字体大师 Erik Spiekermann 与德国概念品牌 Unamono 联合推出了一系列围巾和口袋巾，其设计主题为“可穿戴的好艺术”，Erik Spiekermann 把网格图案带到了绵绸混纺的面料上，颜色均取自 CMYK 基础值，同时穿插进了虚线，整个围巾看起来就像一个方格草稿纸，而精确到厘米的方格的确可以当作真正的尺子来使用。目前围巾售价 129 欧元，<a href=\"http://www.unamono.com/en/\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235514Q481foLRx6ECG2b9.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235515fV543SRCAotEraLM.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.70285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235515AuHps9QhBaqO8vtW.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.38933333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235516ZDFYtCaIGXBToScU.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.39920424\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235516dGgvKeUtl0ExuIXk.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.32637076\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235517r60hB1sX2C3Rj5pD.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235517oI8pMfVTkOGUlSgq.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235518yV52Qz9jaDN3urxX.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}